87
00:05:19,187 --> 00:05:20,027
Yan He.

88
00:05:21,147 --> 00:05:21,987
This time,

89
00:05:22,747 --> 00:05:24,187
let me go with you.

90
00:05:25,306 --> 00:05:28,067
I went along with troops before.

91
00:05:29,666 --> 00:05:30,627
