94
00:05:36,866 --> 00:05:37,706
Besides,

95
00:05:38,387 --> 00:05:39,507
as a general's wife,

96
00:05:40,106 --> 00:05:41,907
I can endure hardships.

97
00:05:44,267 --> 00:05:45,107
