124
00:08:41,267 --> 00:08:43,467
General Yan has fought nonstop
for two days.

125
00:08:45,787 --> 00:08:47,027
- Mai.
- Yes.

126
00:08:47,027 --> 00:08:47,987
You go tell Li Kuang

127
00:08:48,186 --> 00:08:49,387
